oseph-Okpako_WireImage.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Matthew-Followill-and-Caleb-Followill-of-Kings-of-Leon.-CREDIT_-Joseph-Okpako_WireImage.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Matthew-Followill-and-Caleb-Followill-of-Kings-of-Leon.-CREDIT_-Joseph-Okpako_WireImage-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Matthew-Followill-and-Caleb-Followill-of-Kings-of-Leon.-CREDIT_-Joseph-Okpako_WireImage-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Matthew-Followill-and-Caleb-Followill-of-Kings-of-Leon.-CREDIT_-Joseph-Okpako_WireImage-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Matthew-Followill-and-Caleb-Followill-of-Kings-of-Leon.-CREDIT_-Joseph-Okpako_WireImage-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Matthew-Followill-and-Caleb-Followill-of-Kings-of-Leon.-CREDIT_-Joseph-Okpako_WireImage-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>尽管场地许可证尚未获得批准， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kings-of-leon">Kings Of Leon</a>即将在卡迪夫举行的演出门票已经开始销售。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li aria-level="1"><b>阅读更多：</b> <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/kings-of-leon-can-we-please-have-fun-3753952"><b>莱昂之王如何恢复自信：“我们还没有准备好放弃”</b></a></li></ul><p>本周早些时候， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kings-of-leon-announce-huge-summer-2025-uk-shows-in-cardiff-and-lytham-3817790">乐队宣布他们将于明年 6 月 29 日在卡迪夫举行的新系列音乐会</a><a href="https://www.depotlive.co.uk/blackweir" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Blackweir Live 中</a>担任主角。</p><p>这是该系列剧中首个已确认的演出，演出地点为布莱克威尔场 (Blackweir Fields)，这是威尔士首府布特公园 (Bute Park) 的延伸部分。预计 2025 年首届活动还将宣布另外三项表演。</p><p>预售门票已于昨天（12 月 4 日）开始销售，但新的活动许可证尚未获得当地议会的批准，当地议会表示需要确保场地“符合所有法律要求”。</p><p>该公园目前的许可证允许举办可容纳 25,000 人的活动，但新的申请旨在将容量增加到 35,000 人。</p><p>据<a href="https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/articles/cwyp9zdqkn8o" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>英国广播公司</em></a>报道，卡迪夫市议会表示，在许可批准之前开始售票是“常见做法”，并且该活动将“巩固卡迪夫作为主要艺术家的音乐中心的地位”。</p><p>他们补充说，正在采取特别措施，防止公园的板球场遭到破坏。</p><p>一般销售将于明天（12 月 6 日） <a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Fblackweir-tickets-cardiff%2Fvenue%2F254751" target="_blank" rel="noopener">上午</a>9 点开始。 </p><figure id="attachment_3790384" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3790384" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3790384" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/KingsOfLeon-Joes-Head-Song-For-The-City.jpg" alt="Caleb Followill 与 Kings Of Leon 一起在舞台上现场表演" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/KingsOfLeon-Joes-Head-Song-For-The-City.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/KingsOfLeon-Joes-Head-Song-For-The-City-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/KingsOfLeon-Joes-Head-Song-For-The-City-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/KingsOfLeon-Joes-Head-Song-For-The-City-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/KingsOfLeon-Joes-Head-Song-For-The-City-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/KingsOfLeon-Joes-Head-Song-For-The-City-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3790384" class="wp-caption-text"> Caleb Followill 与 Kings Of Leon 一起现场表演。图片来源：里克·科恩/盖蒂</figcaption></figure><p>除了卡迪夫演出之外，乐队还确认将于 7 月 2 日在兰开夏郡莱瑟姆音乐节上于 2025 年夏季举行另一场演出。</p><p>这是继<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/justin-timberlake">贾斯汀·汀布莱克 (Justin Timberlake)</a> 、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/alanis-morissette">艾拉妮丝·莫莉塞特 (Alanis Morissette)</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/simple-minds">Simple Minds</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/texas">Texas</a>将在 2025 年音乐节上表演之后<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/justin-timberlake-alanis-morissette-simple-minds-and-texas-announced-for-2025-lytham-festival-3796080">宣布的倒数第二场演出</a>。您可以<a href="https://www.ticketmaster.co.uk/tk-maxx-presents-lytham-festival-tickets/artist/1573250?irgwc=1&amp;utm_source=2862475-NME%20Networks%20Media%20Limited&amp;utm_medium=affiliate&amp;utm_campaign=2862475&amp;awtrc=&amp;clickId=xjZw7J18RxyKWAKWVKyp4RZRUkCVXL2pnxpU180&amp;camefrom=CFC_BUYAT_2862475&amp;ircid=7559" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处</a>购买门票。</p><p>在其他新闻中， <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/kings-of-leon-can-we-please-have-fun-3753952">今年早些时候，Kings of Leon 的 Caleb Followill 在接受<i>NME</i>采访时</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/caleb-followill-on-why-he-didnt-want-sex-on-fire-to-be-on-only-by-the-night-3754088">回顾了他与该乐队 2008 年大热单曲“Sex On Fire”的关系</a>。 “我不想把它出现在专辑[ <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/reviews-kings-of-leon-9911-343547">‘Only By The Night’</a> ]中，”他说。 “但我知道这……很好。”</p><p>他继续说道：“我知道它有<i>潜力</i>，但我觉得还有其他歌曲……我立刻就知道：‘每个人都会听到这首歌，但他们不会听[专辑]的其余部分。’”</p><p>鼓手内森·弗洛维尔补充道：“这有点像昵称。有人给了你一个昵称，而你却表现得好像你讨厌它……你的余生都将被这个昵称困住。问问我们的表弟纳乔。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kings-of-leon-cardiff-tickets-go-on-sale-despite-venue-licence-not-being-granted-3819388">尽管未获得场地许可证，Kings Of Leon Cardiff 门票仍开始销售，</a>该门票首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
