in/Getty Images/Dave Simpson/WireImage/Iwi Onodera）" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/reading_2025_line_up.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/reading_2025_line_up-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/reading_2025_line_up-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/reading_2025_line_up-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/reading_2025_line_up-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/reading_2025_line_up-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/reading-leeds-festival-2024">雷丁和利兹 2025 年</a>的首发名单已经公布——查<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/CHAPPELL-ROAN">普尔·罗恩 (Chappell Roan)</a> 、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/TRAVIS-SCOTT">特拉维斯·斯科特 (Travis Scott)</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bring-me-the-horizon">Bring Me The Horizo​​n</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/HOZIER">霍齐尔 (Hozier)</a>都将成为头条新闻。查看到目前为止的完整账单和下面的门票详细信息。</p><ul><li><a href="https://www.nme.com/blogs/nme-blogs/every-reading-leeds-poster-throughout-history-1989934"><strong>阅读更多：</strong>历史上每一张雷丁和利兹队的阵容海报</a></li></ul><p>继<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/liam-gallagher-reading-festival-2024-review-setlist-photos-oasis-reunion-noel-3787153">Liam Gallagher</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/lana-del-rey-reading-2024-live-review-setlist-photos-3786852">Lana Del Rey</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/fred-again-reading-festival-2024-review-photos-setlist-3786905">Fred Again..</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/blink-182-reading-2024-review-photo-setlist-3786510">Blink-182、</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/catfish-the-bottlemen-reading-festival-2024-review-setlist-photos-3787168">Catfish &amp; The Bottlemen</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/gerry-cinnamon-live-at-reading-2024-review-photos-setlist-3786511">Gerry Cinnamon</a>等 2024 年的轰动一时的音乐节之后，明年的双场地音乐节将迎来四位头条新闻，超过其他众多音乐人巨大的名字和冉冉升起的人才。</p><p>查佩尔·罗恩 (Chappell Roan) 的首张专辑《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/chappell-roan-the-rise-and-fall-of-a-midwest-princess-review-debut-album-radar-3499595">中西部公主的兴衰</a>》取得了惊人的缓慢成功，她将在 R&amp;L 上作为英文独家头条新闻亮相，为她的胜利欢呼雀跃。</p><p>特拉维斯·斯科特 (Travis Scott) 将在 2025 年欧洲音乐节上唯一亮相，将他的“乌托邦：马克西姆斯马戏团 (Utopia: Circus Maximus)”巡演的狂野世界带到英国，而《Bring Me The Horizo​​n》将第二次成为头条新闻，他们将继续推出他们著名的 2024 年专辑“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/bring-me-the-horizon-post-human-nex-gen-review-3758948">《后人类：下一代</a>》即将在 2025 年英国音乐节上亮相。 Hozier 也是如此，他将在明年夏天完成 R&amp;L 的四位头条新闻，同时为他的 2023 年大型专辑《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/hozier-unreal-unearth-review-epic-expansive-and-ethereal-3483924">Unreal Unearth</a> 》完成现场表演。</p><p>名单上的其他乐队还有 AJ Tracey、Becky Hill、Sammy Virij、Trippie Redd、Amyl And The Sniffers、Conan Gray、The Kooks、The Dare、Enter Shikari、Wallows、Sea Girls、Mannequin Pussy、SOFT PLAY、Lambrini Girls 、DJ EZ 等等。 Bloc Party 也已确认将在 R&amp;L 2025 上玩首个“Icon Slot”游戏。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DDNTH_QuK2X/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></d